<br>
Examples.   Lets do the Biggy,  Vulak.  Vulak drops alot of class specific loot but caster have it pretty much just a few items for ALL the casters from him.  Make his caster drops include MAJOR spells, Ill list off some ideas for spells. Remember these are biggies so they compare with items like Jaelins Katana but are in no means supposed to be the ONLY idea of spells, just a quick example of idea.  And yes the names of the spells are extremely DORKY :P.  Also being that these are spells they wont have the refresh timers that the AA skills do.<br>
<br>
