Wizard- True Manaburn- 4:1 Ratio manaburn (always 4:1) that still has the chance of critting due to AA skill<br>
Mage- Improved Manifest Elements- pet that is lvl 59, 60 point DS, 7k HP, quad for 135 and has built in Frenzied Burnout (Perment kind of Frenzied Burnout)<br>
